# Claude Code runtime state (ephemeral worktrees, background job data, local machine
# settings) — not part of the project source. Shared config like .claude/skills/,
# .claude/agents/, .claude/commands/, and .claude/settings.json are intentionally
# NOT ignored, since those are meant to be committed and shared with the team.
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/jobs/
.claude/settings.local.json

